With over 40 film and television credits, David continues to be highly sought after in the ultra-competitive Toronto market. He has worked on-camera across the country and on stage in Canada and the US.', dob = '1978-12-17', photo_url = 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sIqdonn5NvUvJoWQbTWO7NDCgE3.jpg'
