    SET biography = N'Malachi dré Beasley (born March 6, 1993) is an actor. He was born and raised in San Diego, California. he later went on to attend the David Geffen School of Drama at Yale University, graduating in 2023. His early rise to attention began during his training at Yale. There, he performed in stage work, including roles such as Justin in Blood at the Root and Pantalone in Commedia through summer programs like Chautauqua Theater Company.

