    SET biography = N'Ben Rosenblatt is a producer of feature films, television series, and short media. Previously an executive at Paramount Pictures and Bad Robot, Ben was Co-Producer on STAR TREK INTO DARKNESS, 10 CLOVERFIELD LANE, and STAR WARS: EPISODE VII - THE FORCE AWAKENS. He was also an Executive Producer of the long running TNT/AMC series Snowpiercer and was a Co-Executive Producer on the Paramount+ series KNUCKLES, the APPLE TV+ series THE BIG CIGAR, and the pilot episode of the HBO Max series TOKYO VICE. Ben has been Emmy Award nominated for his work as Co-Executive Producer on both the TNT series THE ALIENIST and the Netflix series RIPLEY as well as for his work as Executive Producer of the latest installment in Predator franchise, Hulu/20th Century Studios hit film PREY.', dob = null, photo_url = null
