Philnulls work has earned multiple industry accolades, including a VES Award for his groundbreaking animation of Thanos in Avengers: Infinity War. At Digital Domain, he oversaw animation on 43 projects spanning feature films, episodic series, games, and advertising. His credits include major titles such as Deadpool, Endernulls Game, X-Men: Days of Future Past, and Avengers: Endgame, where he served as Animation Director. Earlier in his career, he was also the animation lead on James Cameronulls Avatar at Weta.

Now working full-time as a visual effects supervisor, Phil recently led Digital Domainulls VFX work on Marvel Studiosnull She-Hulk: Attorney at Law. His efforts on the series earned him a VES Award nomination for Best Animated Character and a Silver Telly Award.', dob = null, photo_url = 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p08y3i1cOHTvTegMky102puHWE1.jpg'
