    SET biography = N'Guy Isherwood is a freelance set designer & art director based in London with over 12 years of experience across multiple design fields. He has trained as an architect for 5 years in the UK, gaining bachelornulls and masternulls degrees. His experience includes most recently working as an assistant art director on a Marvel TV show for Disney Plus, an uncredited role in the art department on “Bones” based at Fox Studios, LA, and, for a few years, the in-house art director at JOE Media, designing and managing the sets and visual experiences for their in-house shows and activations.

