UPDATE [dbo].[people]
    SET biography = N'Scott Stokdyk (born October 16, 1969) is an American visual effects artist who is best known for his work on the films Spider-Man and Spider-Man 2.

Stokdyk has won the Academy Award for Best Visual Effects once, with a further two nominations.

