    SET biography = N'Jamie Christopher (22 December 1971 – 29 August 2023) was a British assistant director and film producer. He worked on numerous films, including the Harry Potter series, Guardians of the Galaxy, Avengers: Age of Ultron, and Star Wars: The Last Jedi.

