Since around 2007, he has been based in Germany with TRIXTER, where he supervises visual effects work and oversees both creative and production responsibilities. Among the many memorable sequences he has overseen are the suit-assembly scenes in Iron Man 3 (2013), the first appearance of Ultron Mark One in Avengers: Age of Ultron (2015), and the quantum hopping face-distortions in Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2 (2017).

