    SET biography = N'Hello! My name is Ethan Costanilla, and I am a working actor who specializes in stage/film work. Inullm a freelance at the moment, who is represented by People Store in Atlanta, GA. I recently was in a SAG-AFTRA project and am currently working to be in more. I also have 6 years of stage acting experience, in which Inullve played 10+ leads, and 2 years of film acting experience. Inullm an actor who strives to curate the perfect adaptation of any character he is given.', dob = '2004-04-13', photo_url = 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dsdFTHLLdqFpipyPX7bWNBRk7hE.jpg'
