Hill has provided voices for the animated films Horton Hears a Who! (2008), Megamind (2010), How to Train Your Dragon (2010–2019), The Lego Movie (2014), and The Lego Movie 2: The Second Part (2019).', dob = '1983-12-20', photo_url = 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cymlWttB83MsAGR2EkTgANtjeRH.jpg'
