UPDATE [dbo].[people]
    SET biography = N'René Vrábel, a force to be reckoned with, blurs the lines between actor a stun man, bringing a fresh and dynamic perspective to physically demanding roles. His journey began in the realm of medicine, but the magnetic pull of the stage proved too strong to resist, prompting him to abandon his studies and pursue his true passion.

