UPDATE [dbo].[people]
    SET biography = N'Tommy Gormley is a Scottish film director and producer. He is known for his work on the genres of action, drama, and science fiction. Gormley has produced or served as assistant director on films such as Star Trek and Star Wars: The Force Awakens.

