    SET biography = N'Chantal Nong Vo is the Executive Vice President of Production at DC Studios.

Before ascending to this leadership role, she served as Vice President for Feature Development and Production at Warner Bros., where she contributed to films such as Crazy Rich Asians (2018), The Meg (2018), The Intern (2015), Godzilla (2014), and 300: Rise of an Empire (2014).

