    SET biography = N'Kimberly Patrick is a sound editor, sound designer, and foley artist for film and television. She grew up in Bowie, Maryland, a suburb east of Washington, D.C. She has a B.A. in music from the University of Maryland, Baltimore County, and an M.F.A. in film and television production from USC.

