His film career would span almost forty years and encompass over 90 films, mostly in small or supporting roles, although with an occasional starring role, as in 1940nulls Zanzibar.

His final acting credit was the 1977 science fiction horror film Empire of the Ants.

Fadden died of natural causes on April 14, 1980 in Vero Beach, Florida.', dob = '1895-01-06', photo_url = 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5fZfgiaVkVfYrt4dG44CngwFGM.jpg'
