UPDATE [dbo].[people]
    SET biography = N'Daniel Michael DeVito Jr. (born November 17, 1944) is an American actor, comedian, director, and producer. He first gained prominence as the irascible dispatcher Louie De Palma on Taxi, for which he won a Golden Globe and an Emmy. He plays Frank Reynolds on the long-running sitcom Itnulls Always Sunny in Philadelphia (2006 - present).

