Gillet publicly shares on social media that his partner is musician, singer and actor Brice Michelini from Cannes who appeared in Rebecca Zlotowskinulls Planétarium (2016). When asked why he chose to write the song Andy, I Love You (French: Andy, Je Tnullaime) and have him acting in the music video, Michelini declared: "Because I love Andy. Andy, henulls the man I love. This name came to me before I even made music. Andy is a muse: not just mine, a lot of peoplenulls muse. For me it was a waste to live with a muse and not do anything with it."

